<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main/main.css">
{{> layout/header}}

<main>
    <div class="banner-wrap">
        <button class="banner-btn prev">&lt;</button>
        <div class="banner">
            <div class="banner-track">
                <div class="banner-slide">
                    <img src="/img/main/space.png" alt="배너 1">
                </div>
                <div class="banner-slide">
                    <img src="/img/main/chrismas.png" alt="배너 2">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="banner-btn next">&gt;</button>
    </div>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="section-title">새로운 공간</div>
        <div class="space-list">
            {{#place}}
                <a href="/place/{{id}}/room" class="space-card">
                    <div class="space-img">
                        <img src="{{profilePath}}" alt="장소사진" class="space-img">
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-name">
                        <h4>{{name}}</h4>
                        <p><img src="/img/main/mainPlace.png" alt=""> 주소 : {{address}}</p>
                        <p>카테고리 : {{category}}</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            {{/place}}
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="section-title">진행중인 이벤트</div>
        <div class="event-list">
            <div class="event-card left-img">
                <p>연말 모임, 선택은 간단하게!<br>어울림 파티룸과 함께하세요.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="event-card right-img">
                <p>연습, 모임, 공연 준비까지<br>어울림 연습실에서 한 번에 해결하세요.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="section-title">방금 올라온 후기</div>
            <div class="review-grid">
            {{#reviews}}
                <div class="review-card">
                    <div class="review-header">
                        <div class="review-user">
                            <p class="user-name">{{name}}</p>
                            <p class="user-star">{{#stars}}★{{/stars}}{{#emptyStars}}☆{{/emptyStars}}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="review-content">{{content}}</p>
                </div>
            {{/reviews}}
            </div>

        {{^reviews}}
            <div>아직 등록된 리뷰가 없습니다.</div>
        {{/reviews}}
    </section>

    <section>
    <!-- chatBot -->
<!--        <div class="chat-popup" id="chat-popup" aria-hidden="true">-->
<!--            <div class="header">-->
<!--                <h1>ChatBot</h1>-->
<!--                <button class="btn-close" id="btn-close" type="button" aria-label="닫기">✕</button>-->
<!--            </div>-->

<!--            <div class="chat-box" id="chat-box"></div>-->

<!--            <form class="input-area" id="chat-form">-->
